high_descs: Move forward, then turn right at the counter adjacent to the fridge.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, chill it, then take the tomato out.
Return to the counter to your right.
Place the tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool tomato on the counter.

high_descs: go to the end of the counter on the right and turn to the right facing the counter top
pick up the tomato from the counter top
turn to the left and take few steps and turn to the right facing the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and put the tomato on the shelf and close the door and wait and open the door and take out the tomato and close the refrigerator door
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the left facing the counter top
put the tomato on the counter top right of the spatula
anns.task_desc: Place a cold tomato on the counter top

high_descs: Move forward past the sink on your right, turn right to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Bring the tomato to the fridge on the left.
Cool the tomato in the fridge.
Bring the cooled tomato to the counter, right of the fridge, left of the stove.
Put the cooled tomato on the front right of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato on the counter.
